<!channel> hey all! i know that abby and jenna did a formal regroup on this, but moving forward i'm happy to share any info as compass evolves and changes. just hit me up if you've got questions, concerns, or just want to know how things are going. i'll be reaching out to a few of you to give updates!

also, just a heads up that the adidas design/ux team is charging ahead on implementing updates from UAT feedback, looking forward to new features, and is generally pretty heads down so if we have questions or *need* to ping their team, route whatever you can through me, <@U0261PCRQ>, and <@U3M4RRNQ5> (we can probably get you faster answers :wink: )
